Gia is a 1998 biographical HBO film about the life and times of one of America 's first supermodels , Gia Marie Carangi .
The film stars Angelina Jolie as Gia and Faye Dunaway as Wilhelmina Cooper , with Mercedes Ruehl and Elizabeth Mitchell .
It was directed by Michael Cristofer and written by Cristofer and Jay McInerney .
The original music score was composed by Terence Blanchard .